OL,3,CMum 'heartbroken' as visa rules stop
OL,4,CEgyptian partner meeting newborn baby
OL,6,FA mother says a tightening of visa
OL,7,Frules is preventing her Egyptian
OL,8,Fpartner joining her and their newborn
OL,9,Fdaughter in the UK.
OL,11,FBack in April, the government
OL,12,Fincreased the annual salary needed to
OL,13,Fbring spouses into the country from
OL,14,F#18,500 to #29,000, in a bid to reduce
OL,15,Fimmigration.
OL,17,FTaylor Fitzpatrick, from Farnborough
OL,18,Fin Hampshire, says it would be
OL,19,Fimpossible for her to earn that amount
OL,20,Fof money while she's on maternity
OL,21,Fleave.
