OL,3,CMum 'heartbroken' as visa rules stop
OL,4,CEgyptian partner meeting newborn baby
OL,6,FTaylor said: "It's been a lot. I mean,
OL,7,Fhaving to go through the birth on your
OL,8,Fown and even just the day to day life
OL,9,Fof me having to stay here at home on
OL,10,Fmy own, which normally I know other
OL,11,Fpeople do which is fine, but they have
OL,12,Ftheir partner who comes back home and
OL,13,Fgoes 'Oh well why don't I do this for
OL,14,Fyou or why don't you go for a sleep'
OL,15,Fand it's me 24/7."
OL,17,FTaylor and her partner Hady Magdy met
OL,18,Fwhen they were working as singers in
OL,19,FEgypt three years ago.
