OL,3,CMum 'heartbroken' as visa rules stop
OL,4,CEgyptian partner meeting newborn baby
OL,6,FShe returned to the UK in February
OL,7,Fwith plans to organise a two year
OL,8,Fspouse visa for Hady but soon after
OL,9,Fshe found out she was pregnant and
OL,10,Fcould no longer earn the minimum
OL,11,F#29,000 salary required to sponsor a
OL,12,Fforeign partner.
OL,14,FHady was also denied entry on a
OL,15,Fvisitor visa to be there for the birth
OL,16,Fof his daughter Talia. Instead, he's
OL,17,Fforced to used technology to spend
OL,18,Ftime with her virtually.
