OL,3,CMum 'heartbroken' as visa rules stop
OL,4,CEgyptian partner meeting newborn baby
OL,6,FHady said: "This is not fair because
OL,7,Fthese moments won't happen anymore you
OL,8,Fknow. There is no compensation for me
OL,9,Fto deal with these moments again you
OL,10,Fknow."
OL,12,FTaylor said: "It's bitter sweet
OL,13,Fbecause he's on the phone smiling and
OL,14,Flaughing because he's getting to enjoy
OL,15,Fthese moments with us however it's not
OL,16,Fthe same as him actually enjoying the
OL,17,Fmoments face to face.
OL,19,F"It's heartbreaking watching her look
OL,20,Fat her dad through the telephone, we
OL,21,Fjust want him to be with us."
