OL,6,FThe Home Office said it does not
OL,7,Fcomment on individual cases.
OL,9,FTaylor plans to take Talia to Egypt to
OL,10,Fmeet her dad in person in December.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, she's stuck on her own
OL,13,Ftrying to look after her baby and find
OL,14,Fa job that pays enough to get Hady to
OL,15,Fthe UK.
